	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(center)"><hi rend="underline">In haste</hi></p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><placeName>Buff Bay</placeName> <date>29<hi rend="sup">th</hi> June 37</date></p>
				<p>Reverend Friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Since closing your letter&#44; which I here send you&#44; I reced<lb/> a letter from our friend <persName>M Peixotto</persName>&#44; with yours enclosed bearing<lb/> date <date>7<hi rend="sup">th</hi> May</date>&#44; by which I was glad to hear you were well &#38; hearty.<lb/>  I have long ere this released you of any blame respecting<lb/> the tuition of my Brother in Law&#44; &#38; <sic>Iam</sic> almost satisfied<lb/> that I shall sufficiently satisfy my Father&#39;s Son&#44; that the<lb/> fault lays with the unaccountable eccentricities of<lb/> my friend <persName>Mr P.</persName>  But it is hard that you should be blamed<lb/> for this&#44; &#38; rather than an honest declaration&#44; that you<lb/> should be spoken of in such a way&#44; as <del>to</del> would tend to<lb/> show that your religious feeling is not of that kind it ought<lb/> to be.  Alas&#33;  I know the sting of <sic>persicution</sic> &#38; sarcasms too<lb/> <add>&#63;</add> to swallow all such <sic>indigestable</sic> matter&#33;  You are<lb/> <add>&#63;</add> &#38; where my voice can declare it&#44; believe me<lb/> despite of malice&#44; I will echo the truth&#44; let the result be<lb/> what it may.  I know too well your trouble &#38; labor&#59;<lb/> I have I believe spoken to you of your several works&#59; in the<lb/> <sic>inclosed</sic> letter&#44; therefore have not much more to say&#8212;only<lb/> God speed you in your exertions for our good.<lb/> I thought the <persName>Revd M Nathan</persName> had long paid&#8212;But I will<lb/> not omit asking in plain English&#44; for he does not seem<lb/> to understand <hi rend="underline">hints</hi>&#44; it is too bad&#44; But I will <add>&#63;</add> him &#39;till he pays.<lb/>  Excuse my detaining you so long <del>for</del> with the amount of<lb/> your Books&#44; but I could not write before this.<lb/>  God <add>&#63;</add> you&#44; &#38; give you the desires of<lb/> your heart for good&#8212;is the wish of</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">your dear Friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">W W Sollas</persName></p>
		</body>
